{"id": "1196924521576419448", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 19, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "毫不谦虚地说，即便是在逆转回合内，我的理论分析也算学术前沿。🤓", "timestamp": "2024-01-16T21:10:43.726000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1187277004832251918"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1196859672506941550", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1196925156262674473", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "我承认咱们的PVP模式只是对逆转回合的拙劣模仿（悲）", "timestamp": "2024-01-16T21:13:15.047000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1196925378279776296", "channel_id": "1188546911662252092", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "但这个模式有非常大的潜力，如果支持的人多的话，在精心开发后可以成为非常有意思的玩法。", "timestamp": "2024-01-16T21:14:07.980000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1188546911662252092", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "长期盖楼《PVP理论与内容分析》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1196937328485208064", "channel_id": "1196937328485208064", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "本着评分标准应该体现玩家技术和实力的原则。我认为【一命通关】项的扣分标准太低，使之有漏洞可钻。\n\n因为应急灵知体的效果可以回复所有血量并充满4个人的狂气，因此在使用灵知体后迅速通关可以确保获得【剩余生命】项的分数加成，且足以抵消一命通关的扣分效果。这对于叠加死扛且正常通关的玩家来说并不公平。不能公平反应出实力和水准。\n\n更有甚者，特殊成就会要求在一回合内释放四个人的狂气大招，或者给予boss单回合的高伤害等。这些成就也可以简单通过灵知体辅助完成，且加分项远超减分效果。\n\n综上所述，希望官方能够改善幻梦深潜的评分标准，使之更为合理。", "timestamp": "2024-01-16T22:01:37.131000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1196937328900460574", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 382722, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196937328485208064/1196937328900460574/image.png?ex=69cc4441&is=69caf2c1&hm=6f8c01c6a2339089113bf38946184149def23cffeebdfc2b233dc085548e53c0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1196937328485208064", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」幻梦深潜评分标准中的不合理项：一命通关。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497", "1181168197425172480", "1181168183319736412"]}
{"id": "1196950965740384338", "channel_id": "1196950965740384338", "type": 0, "author_id": "843499496322760717", "author_name": "timgwet_", "author_bot": false, "content": "P1-雷婭啟靈說明：應為「苦痛『與』歡愉」。\nP2-抱歉忘記第五章哪關的主線：應為「亦將」。\n「抑」作連詞表「還是」、「或者」之意，用於「抑或」一詞；此處使用「亦」表「也」意或許較為通順。\nP3-抱歉忘記第五章哪關的主線：建議修正為「釐清」。", "timestamp": "2024-01-16T22:55:48.506000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1196950966566658128", "filename": "Screenshot_20240117_054303.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 107533, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196950965740384338/1196950966566658128/Screenshot_20240117_054303.jpg?ex=69cc50f4&is=69caff74&hm=da282201116bd093339260fa38233c4a6ff8cb1f23a3b754f4f393c3577003e2&"}, {"id": "1196950966906404925", "filename": "Screenshot_20240103_035115.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 142210, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196950965740384338/1196950966906404925/Screenshot_20240103_035115.jpg?ex=69cc50f4&is=69caff74&hm=2e56862a1e7f04919ac5e0efe3625d43ad030d34ddb9af009d4119fa6366c8ac&"}, {"id": "1196950967174836224", "filename": "Screenshot_20231229_224312.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 143884, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196950965740384338/1196950967174836224/Screenshot_20231229_224312.jpg?ex=69cc50f4&is=69caff74&hm=a7dec7e6ecf44f2cec46ee009fb2583270c2134552ac8c222ec599f31e8e43d8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1196950965740384338", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」文字植入錯誤", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
