{"id": "1196608379095879710", "channel_id": "1196608379095879710", "type": 0, "author_id": "1031853039558070354", "author_name": "zhang3xuan2", "author_bot": false, "content": "能否在點選技能的時候\n連同金色技能框一起 放大 ，\n這樣在看技能的時候不會因為字體小而傷眼睛，\n讓玩家眼睛舒適感謝。", "timestamp": "2024-01-16T00:14:29.485000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1196608379519516743", "filename": "Screenshot_20240116_081046.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 145707, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196608379095879710/1196608379519516743/Screenshot_20240116_081046.jpg?ex=69cc6365&is=69cb11e5&hm=56ed56bf976eb51c794ea8a99f708abe39b1c130eeefcff98065837d978f1d30&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1196608379095879710", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」技能內容字體過小", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
